commit message:
Cache distance calculations

There are a fair number of repetitive distance calculations that
need spherical trig to compute. Added a LRU cache for recent
calculations on each position pair to reduce the CPU resources
needed.

Signed-off-by: Tod Fitch <Tod@FitchDesign.com>
